 situation.</li>				<li>Always use protective glasses and or face shields as recommended in ANSI Standard Z87.1 flange.</li>				<li>If you have any questions concerning the overall safety of a particular application consult your foreman or your safety department.</li>            </ul>                    </div><!--col-left-->                <div class="col-right">        <?php include_once ('includes/r-flapwheels.php'); ?>        <?php include_once ('includes/hp-right.php'); ?>	        </div><!--col-right--><?php include_once ('includes/footer.php'); ?>        